  <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Sound recordings documenting three significant periods in Ferguson's career. Discs in Series I (1939-1941) record statements taken for the Wayne County Graft Grand Jury; discs in Series II (1956-1959, and undated) record dictation drafts of letters, opinions, conference notes, and memos regarding Ferguson's service to the U.S. Court of Military Appeals. The tape records an address Ferguson gave in the Philippines in honor of Rizal Day, Jan. 6, 1967.</subfield>
